OL,6,FIn some cities across the UK, rioters
OL,7,Fhad set fire to hotels housing asylum
OL,8,Fseekers, and launched bricks and
OL,9,Ffireworks at police.
OL,11,FFor Mohsan Ishaq, the riots last month
OL,12,Fstill remain on his mind.
OL,14,F"It does worry me, like if this
OL,15,Fhappened, could it happen again? God
OL,16,Fforbid, we don't want something like
OL,17,Fthat," he said.
