OL,6,FAround the mid-1980s, he moved to
OL,7,FNorth Tyneside to open a corner shop.
OL,8,FIt was just a few years later that he
OL,9,Fexperienced the Meadow Well estate
OL,10,Friots.
OL,12,FUnrest broke out on the North Tyneside
OL,13,Festate on the night of 9 September
OL,14,F1991.
OL,16,FThe violence was sparked after the
OL,17,Fdeaths of two joyriders, Dale Robson,
OL,18,F17, and Colin Atkins, 21. They were
OL,19,Fkilled when their stolen car went out
OL,20,Fof control while being chased by
OL,21,Fpolice at high speed.
