OL,9,Fclaims, it stirred anti-police
OL,10,Fsentiment in the area.
OL,12,FHundreds of people went on to loot
OL,13,Fshops, vandalise buildings and pelt
OL,14,Fbricks at emergency services.
OL,16,FViolence had also spread from North
OL,17,FTyneside to Newcastle - with business
OL,18,Fand homes in the West End also
OL,19,Ftargeted.
